skills.title: Cloud Computing
skills.description: Gained a strong foundation in cloud technologies through comprehensive training in Amazon Web Services (AWS) and successful completion of the Google Cloud Career Practitioner and Google Gen-AI labs. Applied this knowledge across various projects, demonstrating proficiency in cloud-based solutions.

skills.title: Data Structure and Algorithm
skills.description: Currently enhancing my expertise in DSA, having mastered key topics such as Arrays, Object-Oriented Programming (OOPs), and Linked Lists. I have solved over 150 problems on LeetCode, consistently refining my skills and deepening my understanding of complex algorithms.

skills.title: Web Development
skills.description: Acquired robust web development skills and successfully built a responsive website using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Demonstrated these abilities through a hands-on project, showcasing proficiency in front-end development and design.

skills.title: Leadership & Community Management:
skills.description: Leveraged my leadership skills by managing college coding communities such as Google Developer Students Club (GDSC) and ACM. Currently, I contribute to IEEE, where I have successfully organized and hosted numerous webinars and coding competitions, fostering a collaborative and innovative environment.
